@startuml
title Lab 6 Part 2 - Weighted Average Window
left to right direction

rectangle "Newest sample\nx[n]\nweight 50" as S0
rectangle "Previous sample\nx[n-1]\nweight 25" as S1
rectangle "Older sample\nx[n-2]\nweight 15" as S2
rectangle "Oldest sample\nx[n-3]\nweight 10" as S3
rectangle "Weighted sum / 100\nfinal average" as AVG

S0 --> AVG
S1 --> AVG
S2 --> AVG
S3 --> AVG

note bottom of AVG
average =
(50*x[n] + 25*x[n-1] +
15*x[n-2] + 10*x[n-3]) / 100
end note

@enduml
